Faith Family Church wishes you a very Merry Christmas!  We had a wonderful Christmas celebration yesterday and we want to thank everyone who helped make it possible.  Be Blessed!

<a href="http://ffc-upstate.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/2012-12-23-11.30.46.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-693" title="2012-12-23 11.30.46" src="http://ffc-upstate.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/2012-12-23-11.30.46-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>

